  "prompt": "If I have someone blocked on Instagram, and view their story, can they see I viewed it?",
  "response": "No, if you have someone blocked on Instagram, they cannot see that you viewed their story. When you block someone, it prevents them from seeing your profile, posts, and stories, and vice versa. Thus, you cannot view their stories while they are blocked. If you unblock them, your past story views won't be visible to them either.",
